#### Description (usage)

This API allows the return of multiple Domo Entities

**UI reference**

N/A

#### **Resources**

N/A

#### Required parameters

**{ combineResults:False }** - will return add a nested key-value pair,

**searchResultsMap**, with a dictionary of entity types containing arrays of entities.

The **searchObjects** key will always have an array of results.

The **totalResultCount** key can be used to support building a loop function if you limit the **count** of your responses in the filter body.

*   Query result
